624
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:21,990
God from on high,

625
00:32:22,110 --> 00:32:23,430
hits right into the light of my soul.

626
00:32:23,430 --> 00:32:24,710
I saw similar bombastic compliments

627
00:32:24,710 --> 00:32:26,550
on Qing He's Tieba all the time.

628
00:32:26,630 --> 00:32:27,590
They were all written

629
00:32:27,590 --> 00:32:29,590
