653
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:26,740
Screw it!

654
00:33:28,110 --> 00:33:28,870
What are you doing?

655
00:33:29,790 --> 00:33:32,020
See. Even I'd say this.

656
00:33:32,350 --> 00:33:33,630
An elegant White Swan

657
00:33:33,630 --> 00:33:34,510
