660
00:33:38,870 --> 00:33:39,590
That's not it.

661
00:33:39,670 --> 00:33:40,910
It's not that I don't trust you,

662
00:33:41,230 --> 00:33:42,710
I'm just...

663
00:33:43,070 --> 00:33:45,070
I'm thrilled. I'm too excited.

664
00:33:45,950 --> 00:33:47,390
I have so many questions for you,

665
00:33:47,470 --> 00:33:49,830
