666
00:33:49,870 --> 00:33:50,870
The important thing to do

667
00:33:50,870 --> 00:33:52,310
is solving your issue now.

668
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:54,140
I have to deal with Wang Yi Ming first.

669
00:33:54,350 --> 00:33:56,030
He has a big mouth.

670
00:33:56,270 --> 00:33:58,070
