681
00:34:30,870 --> 00:34:32,830
People have seen everything.

682
00:34:32,949 --> 00:34:34,670
What if they've taken screenshots?

683
00:34:38,699 --> 00:34:40,230
See. I told you!

684
00:34:41,949 --> 00:34:42,590
I'm doomed.

685
00:34:43,389 --> 00:34:45,670
My mum will meet Mr. Jia next Monday.

686
00:34:46,150 --> 00:34:48,550
That will be the end of me.

687
00:34:51,350 --> 00:34:52,190
Calm down first.

688
00:34:52,790 --> 00:34:53,989
I'll analyse it for you.

689
00:34:54,659 --> 00:34:56,710
First, today is weekend.

690
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:58,350
The teachers haven't seen it yet.

691
00:34:58,750 --> 00:35:01,430
Second, this username

692
00:35:01,670 --> 00:35:03,110
has just been registered today.

693
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:07,230
Have you offended anyone recently?

694
00:35:08,950 --> 00:35:10,060
No.

695
00:35:10,500 --> 00:35:12,190
I've just been here for less than a month.

696
00:35:12,230 --> 00:35:13,390
I even acted like that.

697
00:35:13,390 --> 00:35:14,390
Who could I offend?

698
00:35:18,030 --> 00:35:20,870
Could your mailbox have been hacked?

699
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:24,230
That can't be.

700
00:35:24,830 --> 00:35:26,630
