701
00:35:26,830 --> 00:35:28,590
It was just a simple letter.

702
00:35:28,870 --> 00:35:31,230
It was no longer
full of bombastic compliments.

703
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:36,190
These sentences...

704
00:35:40,190 --> 00:35:42,070
