705
00:36:00,550 --> 00:36:01,430
You know what?

706
00:36:02,070 --> 00:36:03,190
This drink is not bad.

707
00:36:03,670 --> 00:36:04,710
I agree.

708
00:36:04,710 --> 00:36:05,230
Right?
